title: Jaruwan Jenjudkarn
text: Jaruwan Jenjudkarn (born 4 July 1970) is a Thai <a href="Sport%20of%20athletics">athlete</a>. She competed in the <a href="Athletics%20at%20the%201992%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20high%20jump">women's high jump</a> at the <a href="1992%20Summer%20Olympics">1992 Summer Olympics</a>.
